        <num>43-9-13</num>
        <content>
          <p>Upon written presentation to the board of any of the grounds enumerated in Code Section 43-9-12 for revoking or refusing a license, the board shall conduct a hearing in conformance with Chapter 13 of Title 50, the "Georgia Administrative Procedure Act."</p>
